%% Diagramme de séquence — upload, enqueue, extraction, règles, SSE (détail)
%% Éditable : Mermaid sequenceDiagram
%% Entrées : api/uploads.py · run_enqueue.py · run_dispatch.py · taskiq · run_processor.py · run_events.py

sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as Utilisateur
  participant UI as Next.js UI
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant PG as PostgreSQL
  participant S3 as MinIO
  participant R as Redis Streams<br/>+ pub/sub SSE
  participant W as Worker extract
  participant VLM as NuExtract<br/>llama-server

  %% Upload
  rect rgb(245, 240, 230)
    Note over U,S3: Upload présigné
    U->>UI: Choisit fichier
    UI->>API: POST /uploads/presign<br/>filename, size, mime
    API->>API: Valide taille / MIME
    API->>PG: record_upload_intent
    API->>S3: presign_put runs/{id}/fichier
    API-->>UI: url, storageKey, uploadId
    UI->>S3: PUT binaire
    S3-->>UI: 200 OK
    UI->>API: POST /uploads/confirm
    API->>S3: HeadObject / stat
    API->>API: Sniff MIME réel
    API->>PG: confirm_upload_intent
    API-->>UI: binding confirmé
  end

  %% Enqueue
  rect rgb(245, 230, 240)
    Note over UI,R: Création run + outbox + Taskiq
    UI->>API: POST /workflows/{id}/runs/json<br/>documentBindings + options
    API->>API: resolve_run_enqueue_source<br/>test JWT vs API key
    API->>API: Rate limit + admission capacité
    API->>API: run_pool_classifier<br/>→ extract si PDF+document_model
    API->>PG: INSERT Run queued<br/>+ RunDocument bindings
    API->>PG: INSERT outbox dispatch
    API-->>UI: 202 { runId }
    API->>API: schedule_outbox_dispatch
    API->>R: task.kiq process-audit-run<br/>queue repody:audit:extract
    Note over PG,R: Outbox Postgres = rejeu durable<br/>si Redis momentanément indisponible
  end

  %% Worker extraction
  rect rgb(255, 244, 224)
    Note over R,VLM: Worker extract
    R->>W: Message Taskiq ACK
    W->>PG: Advisory lock + CAS<br/>queued → running
    W->>R: PUBLISH progress running
    W->>S3: GET objet storageKey
    S3-->>W: bytes PDF/image
    W->>W: DocumentBundle + render pages
    W->>W: catalog parse_document_model<br/>repody:vlm
    W->>VLM: chat.completions<br/>images + template schéma
    VLM-->>W: content JSON champs
    W->>W: parse_fields_json
    W->>PG: Persist ExtractedField
    W->>R: PUBLISH progress extraction
  end

  %% Règles
  rect rgb(238, 246, 232)
    Note over W,PG: Validation
    W->>W: rules/runner validate_extracted
    loop Chaque règle logic
      W->>W: simpleeval sur champs
    end
    opt AUDIT_LLM_VALIDATION_ENABLED
      W->>VLM: Modèle validation texte
      VLM-->>W: pass/fail + motif
    end
    W->>PG: INSERT RuleResult
    W->>PG: UPDATE Run done|failed<br/>overall_status durée
    W->>R: PUBLISH terminal
  end

  %% UI follow
  rect rgb(232, 244, 252)
    Note over UI,API: Suivi UI
    UI->>API: GET /runs/{id}/events
    API->>R: SUBSCRIBE audit:run:progress:{id}
    R-->>API: événements progress
    API-->>UI: SSE data
    UI->>API: GET /runs/{id}?full=true
    API->>PG: Jointure run + docs + fields + rules
    API-->>UI: Rapport complet
    UI-->>U: Affichage audit
  end
